<h2>Maintaining the Eleventy/Handlebars Project</h2>
<p>To keep this project running smoothly, here are some best practices to follow:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Organize Files:</strong> All relevent files are in src and are not to be removed. The dist file can be deleted as the build creates a new one every run. Edit the eleventy.config.js to further customize.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Dependencies Regularly:</strong> Use <code>npm outdated</code> to check for outdated packages, and <code>npm update</code> to keep everything current. This ensures compatibility and access to new features.</li>
    <li><strong>Run the Project Locally:</strong> To see changes live, run the project in development mode using <code>npx @11ty/eleventy --serve</code>. This helps catch any errors early on.</li>
</ul>
